column2: SELECT    m.Name AS Name_cls,n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra, o.dec AS dec,    o.modelMag_u as mu, o.modelMag_g as mg, o.modelMag_r as mr, o.modelMag_i as mi, o.modelMag_z as mz,    c.z as photoZ, c.zErr as photoZErr,    ISNULL(s.z,#) as z,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as zErr,     into mydb.maughan_SDSS_gals_fov from Galaxy as o left outer join SpecObj as s on o.objID = s.bestObjID  join dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq( m.Xra, m.Xdec, m.theta7Mpc) as n on b.objID = o.objID  join Photoz as c on c.objID = p.objID     into mydb.maughan_sdss_rs_b from MyDB.maughan_may_# AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq( m.Xra, m.Xdec, m.theta7Mpc) AS n    JOIN Galaxy AS o ON n.objid = o.objid    JOIN Photoz AS c ON c.objid = o.objid          left outer join SpecObj as s on o.objid = s.bestObjID    WHERE   c.z > # AND      clean = # AND (calibStatus_r & #) != #  SELECT * FROM maughan_sdss_rs        SELECT p.obj, str(p.ra,#,#) as ra, str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec, p.r,p.u,p.g,p.i,p.z, p.petroR5#_g,p.petroR5#_i,p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR9#_g,p.petroR9#_i,p.petroR9#_r, str(p.u - p.g,#,#) as ugModelColor, str(p.g - p.r,#,#) as grModelColor, str(p.r - p.i,#,#) as riModelColor, str(p.i - p.z,#,#) as izModelColor, p.dered_g,p.dered_i,p.dered_r, ISNULL(s.z,#) as z,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as zErr, p.score as score, c.z,c.zErr   into mydb.ZwCl2# from Galaxy as p  left outer join SpecObj as s on p.objID = s.bestObjID  join dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) as b on b.objID = p.objID  join Photoz as c on c.objID = p.objID  WHERE p.g < # AND p.r < # AND p.i < # AND p.z < # AND c.z > # AND c.z < # AND (p.score >= #)
